latestIgtvVideos.title: NEIMAN MARCUS x INCIRCLE December triple point event
latestIgtvVideos.caption: When it comes to holidays, the first thought that comes to mind is guilt-free shopping! 🤷🏻‍♀ Since I love shopping and visit @NeimanMarcus to get outfit inspirations, I decided to make my first IGTV video for their InCircle December Triple Point event, and share some in-store shopping moments and my go-to outfits with you! Through 12/18, as a Neiman Marcus credit card holder and #InCircle member, you’ll receive triple the points on nearly every purchase. Another great benefit that adds to this event is free gift packaging (Circle 3+) – trust me, after you see how they wrap packages, you’ll want to buy all your gifts here.🎄🎁 For more info, check out incircle.com @neimansnyc #NeimanMarcus #ad
